    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolutely wonderful to own. This car is in really great shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It looks sharp, drives smoothly, and is ready to hit the road with a new owner today! I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and a factory-spec M-Variable differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates with factory precision. Equipped with the Competition Package\u2019s quicker steering rack and cross-drilled rotors, this driver-focused example offers an authentic analog experience with balanced damping and communicative turn-in.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well.",
